name: SubnetCalculator

skdetail:

Invocation Name: subnet calculator
des: Currently, this skill provides the subnet mask for a given network prefix (in slash notation). Future updates will provide network and broadcast address for a given host address, as well as other subnet calculations.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
